OL,3,CInquest to open into baby found under
OL,4,Cfloorboards during renovation
OL,6,FAn inquest is due to open into the
OL,7,Fdeath of a baby whose remains were
OL,8,Fdiscovered by workmen renovating a
OL,9,Fbuilding in County Durham.
OL,11,FThe skeleton of the infant was found
OL,12,Fwrapped in newspaper in an upstairs
OL,13,Fflat on Fore Bondgate, in Bishop
OL,14,FAuckland, on 29 July 2024.
OL,16,FIt has now been confirmed that an
OL,17,Finquest will be heard by Jeremy
OL,18,FChipperfield at Crook Coroner's Court
OL,19,Fon Tuesday 14 April.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
