CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1775056271
OL,3,CInquest to open into baby found under
OL,4,Cfloorboards during renovation
OL,6,FFollowing the discovery of the
OL,7,Fremains, the Bishop Auckland property
OL,8,Fundergoing renovations was attended by
OL,9,Fpolice and CSI teams.
OL,11,FOfficers confirmed at the time that
OL,12,Fthe circumstances surrounding its
OL,13,Fdeath were likely to be suspicious.
OL,15,FAt one stage, the building housed a
OL,16,Fchurch-run mother-and-baby unit,
OL,17,Falthough it is believed that the baby
OL,18,Fwas concealed before then.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
